OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,For thunderstorms easing and skies
OL,7,Fclearing to leave a fine, dry night.
OL,8,FWarm overnight for many eastern areas,
OL,9,Falthough feeling slightly fresher in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FSome early sunshine likely,
OL,13,Falthough cloud increasing from the
OL,14,Fwest brings a risk of showers, perhaps
OL,15,Fthundery. A slightly cooler day for
OL,16,Fmany areas, but still generally very
OL,17,Fwarm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
